<paragraph blockId="25.[151,1437,428,815]" pageId="25" pageNumber="86">
Originally described from 
<collectingCountry box="[448,520,428,454]" name="Brazil" pageId="25" pageNumber="86">Brazil</collectingCountry>
. Also reported from 
<collectingCountry box="[747,861,428,454]" name="Argentina" pageId="25" pageNumber="86">Argentina</collectingCountry>
, 
<collectingCountry box="[873,958,428,454]" name="Bolivia" pageId="25" pageNumber="86">Bolivia</collectingCountry>
, and 
<collectingCountry box="[1016,1120,429,455]" name="Paraguay" pageId="25" pageNumber="86">Paraguay</collectingCountry>
(
<bibRefCitation author="Oliva, A." box="[1135,1272,428,455]" pageId="25" pageNumber="86" pagination="301 - 341" refId="ref12740" refString="Oliva, A. (1996) The genus Hydrochus Leach (Coleoptera: Hydrophiloidea: Hydrochidae) in South America, with special reference to Argentina. Bulletin et annales de la Societe royale belge d'entomologie, 132, 301 - 341." type="journal article" year="1996">Oliva, 1996</bibRefCitation>
); however, additional confirmation of the records from 
<collectingCountry box="[623,734,464,490]" name="Argentina" pageId="25" pageNumber="86">Argentina</collectingCountry>
and 
<collectingCountry box="[792,874,464,490]" name="Bolivia" pageId="25" pageNumber="86">Bolivia</collectingCountry>
are needed. Confirmation of the 
<collectingCountry box="[1252,1356,465,491]" name="Paraguay" pageId="25" pageNumber="86">Paraguay</collectingCountry>
record (
<taxonomicName authorityName="Makhan" authorityYear="1995" box="[161,415,500,526]" class="Insecta" family="Hydrochidae" genus="Hydrochus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="25" pageNumber="86" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="johannapietersenae">
<emphasis box="[161,415,500,526]" italics="true" pageId="25" pageNumber="86">H. johannapietersenae</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
jr. syn.) was given in 
<bibRefCitation author="Perkins, P. D." box="[661,842,500,527]" pageId="25" pageNumber="86" pagination="149 - 167" refId="ref12800" refString="Perkins, P. D. (2019 a) Type designations for Neotropical water beetles in the genus Hydrochus Leach, 1817. (Coleoptera: Hydrochidae). Zootaxa, 4701 (2), 149 - 167. https: // doi. org / 10.11646 / zootaxa. 4701.2.2" type="journal article" year="2019">Perkins (2019a)</bibRefCitation>
. Locality and deposition data records have been published for 
<collectingCountry box="[263,356,536,562]" name="Ecuador" pageId="25" pageNumber="86">Ecuador</collectingCountry>
(
<bibRefCitation author="Perkins, P. D." box="[370,537,536,563]" pageId="25" pageNumber="86" pagination="358 - 374" refId="ref13023" refString="Perkins, P. D. (2020 b) Taxonomy of Ecuadorian water beetles in the genus Hydrochus Leach, 1817 (Coleoptera: Hydrochidae). Zootaxa, 4790 (2), 358 - 374. https: // doi. org / 10.11646 / zootaxa. 4790.2.10" type="journal article" year="2020">Perkins 2020b</bibRefCitation>
). Records from 
<collectingCountry box="[714,765,537,563]" name="Peru" pageId="25" pageNumber="86">Peru</collectingCountry>
are given below. Habitus and male genitalia illustrations are given in 
<bibRefCitation author="Perkins, P. D." box="[249,431,572,599]" pageId="25" pageNumber="86" pagination="149 - 167" refId="ref12800" refString="Perkins, P. D. (2019 a) Type designations for Neotropical water beetles in the genus Hydrochus Leach, 1817. (Coleoptera: Hydrochidae). Zootaxa, 4701 (2), 149 - 167. https: // doi. org / 10.11646 / zootaxa. 4701.2.2" type="journal article" year="2019">Perkins (2019a)</bibRefCitation>
.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
